<D>__{well, i think }
<C>__{mr. henry}
<D>__{no, if i go out on this job, then it's just another score by mr. henry. and i don't see it like that. this is your job. your creation. i want you to try this.}
<A>__{they all try the wine. mr. henry watches their reactions.}
<C>__{anthony}
<D>__{this is good.}
<C>__{mr. henry}
<D>__{i want to ask a favor, boys. one day, when i'm long gone and all but forgotten, make one last toast to abe henry. and remember me as a friend.}
